The paper discusses the visualization and analysis of citation networks, which is a topic related to digital libraries (cs.DL) and information retrieval (cs.IR). The use of citation impact measures and the study of interdisciplinary developments also suggest sub-categories such as social and information networks (cs.SI), software engineering (cs.SD), and cybernetics (cs.CY).
